Package project.testmaster.backend.configuration

package project.testmaster.backend.configuration
This package contains configuration classes for the TestMaster backend application.

The configuration classes in this package are responsible for setting up various aspects of the application, such as security, environment-specific properties, and other application-wide settings.

  • EnvConfig - Configuration class for environment-specific properties.
  • SecurityConfig - Security configuration class for setting up security-related configurations.
